{"tid":2210463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃藝人 出新歌  內容關於手足","createTime":"2020-09-20T12:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T03:49:21.000Z","uid":33586,"like":143,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"23e3842966732fdb04e36710cdf8e426d29c7376","tid":2210463,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"除咗黃色經濟圈之外，有啲人問點解藝人全撚部都唔敢出聲<br />\n主要係想賺人民幣，而唔出聲 <br />\n當然有部分係仆街啦 例如廢老倫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果香港人養得起自己嘅藝人，個情況可能會有改善<br />\n<br />\n講咁多都係想介紹一位歌手叫 <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">李芷君</span></span><br />\n之前都出過首 <span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">赴湯蹈火</span></span><br />\n<br />\n近排佢同黃到金嘅作詞人 <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">梁栢堅</span></span> 出咗首歌比 在囚手足 叫<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">解悶工廠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首歌近日派咗台 而家得9千幾click rate<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/31fClz9Ig-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F31fClz9Ig-s&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2Omq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=9516c835\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/31fClz9Ig-s</a><br />\n<br />\n想咁多位手足 幫個手推高reach rate <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果可以 更加希望下年頭推到拎獎<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3237779492943383&amp;id=2107034039351273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3237779492943383%26id%3D2107034039351273&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2Omq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=6798fd53\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3237779492943383&amp;id=2107034039351273</a>"},{"pid":"e41fb7bf555a0425fd7f89a533f3cea1086b3218","tid":2210463,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ac8f66379e91e4bccc1dd562286e9