pid":"8aca4da14d65d15416d74c158f09d8e7a029a761","tid":2210463,"uid":306949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a6fe9d00eba3566a8bbfeb076d1c3959fa4ef4","tid":2210463,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e79ff5111c8bad33c4912644b52a1b9398f196ee","tid":2210463,"uid":210794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wN01t5_VoG8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwN01t5_VoG8&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2Omq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=14c29792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wN01t5_VoG8</a><br />\n<br />\n推埋赴湯蹈火！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f33098e6b24a40a7e6036e800366f7117d4625d","tid":2210463,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa01f1b6221c909f41152c615a6317e6332f5bc","tid":2210463,"uid":345573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"83358796602fa56b51036f5db5a0e3dc4bdd24d1","tid":2210463,"uid":33586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一年前大家一齊行出嚟反送中，<br />\n係因為唔信任支那，<br />\n認為佢哋會為政治目的濫捕濫控，<br />\n送香港人返支那 剝奪晒所有人權，<br />\n逼佢地認罪響支那監禁，<br />\n或交出等價去換取自由。<br />\n<br />\n而今日12位香港人嘅遭遇，<br />\n將普通偷渡罪變成分裂國家。<br />\n出動國家機器迫代表律師退下，夾硬安黨律師做代表。<br />\n面對公眾講大話係12個人意願，但家屬連一面都見唔到。<br />\n然後香港政府只係隻奶屎跟尾狗，<br />\n唔會為香港人維護人權，<br />\n證明左共產黨係唔可信，<br />\n香港人反送中係正確係必須。<br />\n<br />\n但呢件事亦都證明咗送中條例仍然存在，<br />\n只係佢換咗個方式。<br />\n大家可能會覺得係呢12個人自己送上去，<br />\n但其實一切港府都知情，<br />\n蘋果都爆過料話班狗一早知。<br />\n<br />\n大家可能會覺得咁又點，<br />\n嗰12人都已經喺中共手上，<br />\n仲點救仲點去幫？<br />\n但其實從來都唔係有希望先去做呢件事，<br />\n而係做咗先有希望。<br />\n<br />\n開頭幾日大家都好關注，<br />\n所羅門twitter懷疑唔係喺中國海域拉人，<br />\n第九日之鋒叫人保持關注，<br />\n白宮聯署 區議員聯署開始出現，<br />\n家屬開記者會前一日pompeo出聲,<br />\n開始有歐洲國家出聲，<br />\n第二十五日開始有postcard行動，每一區，遠到連長洲都動員得起。<br />\n假如我地係當下一刻只思考到宿命，<br />\n唔願意衝擊宿命對我地既脅迫，<br />\n咁好可能我或者你將會成為第13個係船上既手足。<br />\n<br />\n打咗咁多，大家都可能當我廢噏。<br />\n因為樓主都只係一個識推聯署叫人關注叫人twitter嘅廢柴，<br />\n但我想表達嘅係如果我哋呢刻乜都唔做，<br />\n真係等緊死。<br />\n<br />\n十月一係一個好重要嘅日子，<br />\n十月一可能會係12手足送中第39日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pv7hS7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPv7hS7e.png&h=1fe7427b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實大家都係船上第十三個送中港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2210592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2210592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"879ff51cbfb8ca1d6f8c89c3c73bb5cee040dbc9","tid":2210463,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833c1964811ccc80009f37c2a6268510075496c6","tid":2210463,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0a711fc3e561f969bd711e76a1485bc08498d3","tid":2210463,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.